snippet.title: Disaster Will Strike
snippet.description:
Are you ready to epic battle?! Create natural disasters to smash terrified little eggs!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qaibo.dws

The hit online puzzle game that enjoyed OVER 50 MILLION PLAYS has been revamped and re-engineered for the App Store, bigger and better than ever before!

Are you ready?!  Download the game and don't get shell shock!
